30:38.621 --> 30:41.112
Kitty, kitty! Here, kitty!

30:41.207 --> 30:44.790
Here, kitty! Come on, you fool cat!
Where are you?

30:44.877 --> 30:48.412
Here, pussy cat! Here!

30:48.506 --> 30:50.712
Elmira!

30:56.431 --> 30:58.471
Elmira!

31:01.520 --> 31:05.434
Where are you? That fool cat! Elmira!

31:05.524 --> 31:10.863
Come on, cat! Here, kit, kit, kit, kitty!
Here, kitty! Come on, kitty!

31:11.906 --> 31:17.031
Elmira! Why don't you talk? Darn cat!
You're driving me crazy.

31:17.119 --> 31:18.946
Elmira!

31:30.759 --> 31:32.882
Oh, my God.

31:34.763 --> 31:36.590
Nice kitty.

31:36.681 --> 31:38.508
You bastards!

31:38.600 --> 31:40.676
You dirty little bastards!

31:40.769 --> 31:45.562
You get away from me!
